|Technique=Technique/T1008
|Description={{LinkThisPage}} malware SierraAlfa sends data to one of the hard-coded C2 servers chosen at random, and if the transmission fails, chooses a new C2 server to attempt the transmission again.[[CiteRef::Novetta Blockbuster RATs]]
}}{{Technique Object
|Technique=Technique/T1033
|Description={{LinkThisPage}} malware SierraAlfa and WhiskeyAlfa-Three enumerate logged-on users. {{LinkThisPage}} malware IndiaIndia collects the victim's username and sends it to the C2 server.[[CiteRef::Novetta Blockbuster Loaders]]
